Subject: XCO:0000635
Value: a A hormone cocktail designed to stabilize the circulating levels of the most important sodium-retaining and waterretaining hormones. It contained d-aldosterone (66 ng/kg per min), hydrocortisone (33 ng/kg per min), norepinephrine (333 ng/kg per min) and Arg8-vasopressin acetate (0.17 ng/kg per min).
